Why shouldn't I make it difficult for you?

1565
01:40:23,833 --> 01:40:26,200
Because it won't do you any good,
that's why.

1566
01:40:26,333 --> 01:40:29,576
- I'm going to marry Susan.
- Don't say it again.

1567
01:40:29,708 --> 01:40:31,870
Please don't say it again.

1568
01:40:37,458 --> 01:40:39,791
