01:45:17,583 --> 01:45:20,496
Hello! There you are, Joe.

1619
01:45:20,625 --> 01:45:23,868
So, you're to be leaving us, are you?
Marrying into big business.

1620
01:45:24,000 --> 01:45:27,323
Well, well, congratulations.
What's the matter?

1621
01:45:27,458 --> 01:45:29,745
We were just talking
about the accident, Mr Hoylake.

1622
01:45:29,875 --> 01:45:32,333
- What accident?
- Alice Aisgill's dead.

1623
01:45:32,458 --> 01:45:34,495
Her car crashed last night.

1624
01:45:34,625 --> 01:45:36,287
- No!
- Nasty business.

1625
01:45:36,417 --> 01:45:39,740
I met Dr Everett. He told me.
You knew her well, didn't you, Joe?

1626
01:45:43,542 --> 01:45:45,374
Yes, I knew her.

1627
01:45:45,500 --> 01:45:47,913
