1682
01:49:26,542 --> 01:49:27,953
Jack...

1683
01:49:29,250 --> 01:49:32,322
I've always wanted
to meet someone like you.

1684
01:49:32,458 --> 01:49:34,074
I always have.

1685
01:49:36,708 --> 01:49:39,542
Here, you wouldn't pass out on me?

